metadata.description: Workaholic Atobe Arihito has died and been reborn in 'Labyrinth Country' where he's now a dungeon hunter. He enlists in the guild and picks a job title, but while searching for a party to join, it seems no one wants the help of his bizarre job choice, 'rear support.' He's running out of time to join a group, and when someone finally approaches to offer him a job it's...his ex-boss!? Here starts the adventure of the strongest supporter!
metadata.name: The World's Strongest Rearguard: Labyrinth Country's Novice Seeker
